text:
Nice space for outdoor fun! There's 2 playgrounds (one for younger kids, preschool and another for the older kids).

There's exercise stations located all around the park. Spacious and clean. Good space for cycling too.

Nice and new park. Especially good if you have very young little ones.
A friendly and spacious atmosphere for one and all to enjoy
Huge pirate ship playground with many details and so much fun!
